Well, the internet stuff said it was Treaserur Lynn. But I tried talking to
her and nothing happend. I gave her a ticket and nothing happened.
The quest info said I'm supposed to talk to someone. I talked to everyone
around and nobody would respond.
So I'm basically screwed.
luv,
